      "span_text": "Good clinical results for tigecycline have been demonstrated previously: for example, Bassetti et al. [CITATION_1] showed a 76.5% (13/17) success rate for tigecycline in the treatment of complicated skin and soft tissue infections and an 82.8% (72/87) success rate against peritonitis."
